flowchart LR
IDE["IDE / agent<br/>parent process, orchestrates the action"] ==>|"fork + exec"| H["pretool hook<br/>child process, short-lived<br/>stdin ← request (JSON)<br/>stdout/stderr → diagnostics (does not decide)"]
H ==>|"exit(0 | 2)"| K["KERNEL<br/>holds the status of the finished process"]
K -.->|"wait(): the parent reads the exit code"| IDE
K -.-> N["The decision is the number, never the printed text.<br/>0 = success · ≠0 = failure (POSIX) · 2 = block (agent IDE contract)."]

